  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Keil and Delitzsch Biblical Commentary on the Old Testament",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Consecration of the Priests and the Sanctuary (cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 29:1-37",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). - The consecration of Aaron and his sons as priests was carried out by Moses according to the instructions in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 29:1-36",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
