            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Exodus 30:23",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ".), and the requisite sacrificial offerings (",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Exodus 29:1-3",
            "children": []
          },
          {
